title: #92Noon! LaVelle in for PA!
description: LaVelle E. Neal III fills in for PA and talks Twins and more! The Star Tribune's Chris Hine talks Wolves, Scott Miller of the Bleacher Report shares his perspective on the Skaggs tragedy, and Rochester Red Wings VOX Josh Wetzel gives a Twins AAA update!
